<div class=article>
<div class=editorial>
<div class=editorial>
	<div class=headline>EQ Mini Q&A #1</div>
	<div class=teaser>It was meant for Friday, but today we debut our latest feature! A mini-Q&A about the original EverQuest!</div>
	</div>
